ADDITIONAL NOTES:

Educational Use: This project is for academic research purposes. 

Cultural Sensitivity: Māori language text and cultural content used with 
respect and sensitivity. This project acknowledges Māori data sovereignty 
principles from Te Mana Raraunga.

Wikipedia Content: Documents derived from Wikipedia are used under the 
Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike (CC-BY-SA) license. See 
data/ATTRIBUTION.md for full attribution details.

